Name: assign_user_story_to_sprint
Description: Whether a specific user story is assigned to the target sprint

Name: select_feature_for_release
Description: Whether a feature is included in the upcoming release

Name: assign_task_to_worker
Description: Whether a task is assigned to a particular worker

Name: choose_sprint_for_user_story
Description: Sprint number selected for a user story

Name: decide_team_capacity_story_points
Description: Planned capacity (story points) for the sprint

Name: approve_blocker_resolution
Description: Approval flag that a blocker is resolved and can be closed

Name: schedule_sprint_start_day
Description: Day of month to start the sprint

Name: prioritize_feature_rank
Description: Rank assigned to a feature within the release

Name: budget_allocation_to_project
Description: Allocated budget amount to the project (currency units)

Name: set_sprint_goal_benefit_target
Description: Target benefit score for sprint goal

Name: decide_number_of_tasks_in_sprintbacklog
Description: Number of tasks to include in the sprint backlog

Name: select_stakeholder_for_review
Description: Whether a stakeholder is invited to Sprint Review
